# CLIP ChangeLog for net-misc/stunnel

*stunnel-5.35-r5 (20 Sep 2016)

  20 Sep 2016; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +stunnel-5.35-r5.ebuild, -stunnel-5.35-r4.ebuild:
  Do the vsctl as current user to kill stunnel.

*stunnel-5.35-r4 (05 Sep 2016)

  05 Sep 2016; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +stunnel-5.35-r4.ebuild, -stunnel-5.35-r3.ebuild:
  Modify the init script to handle the case where the rm jails have not been
  updated yet (really).

