*stunnel-4.54-r3 (19 Mar 2013)

  19 Mar 2013; Hugo Chargois <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +stunnel-4.54-r3.ebuild, -stunnel-4.54-r2.ebuild,
  files/stunnel.conf.skel_hermes:
  Allow to specify anything (not just IPs) in the destination
  part of each tunnel configuration. That way, hostnames could
  be configured.

